<li>Thinking of you and your family during this sad time.</li>
<li>Sending heartfelt condolences on the passing of your [relationship to deceased].</li>
<li>May the memories you cherish bring you comfort.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, we offer our thoughts and prayers.</li>
